@NODE 11. "Bugs"
                                Bugs.

	Display:
	         Cause:   listbrowser.gadget V41
	         Problem: Alignment problem between icon/filename to
	                  filesize..
				
	File Menu:
	         Cause:   SunMouse (auto activate window hack)
	         Problem: If using sunmouse, disable it
	                  before using the file menu's.

	www.geocities.com
	         Cause:   www.geocities.com uses a public directory for
	                  all users and doesnt return a list of your
	                  files.
	         Problem: You will never get a list of files in the remote
	                  window and all your files will be uploaded
	                  every time you use it.

	Serv-U FTPD
	         Cause:   Serv-U FTPD for windows and NT doesn't do
	                  recursive directory listings.
	         Problem: No files will show up in sub-directories causing
	                  WebFTP not to compare them correctly.
@ENDNODE

